<inglise>Pursuant to &sect; 2 of the draft Act, &sect; 30 of the Code of Administrative Offences will be amended and limitation periods for administrative offences shall be determined according to the punishment prescribed for the offence and shall be extended upon the entry into force of the Act as follows: </inglise>
