<inglise>On 15 and 16 May, a seminar concerning rights related to copyright was organised for performers, producers of phonograms and broadcasting organisations. </inglise>
<eesti>Nende seminaride sihtgruppide n&auml;ol polnud niiv&otilde;rd tegemist seadusi rakendavate institutsioonidega, kuid k&otilde;igil tasanditel on sellealane temaatika seni v&auml;he k&auml;sitlemist ja tutvustamist leidnud. </eesti>
<inglise>These seminars were not targeted so much at institutions implementing legislation, although the issues have not yet been sufficiently addressed or presented at any level. </inglise>
